{"id": "art-477", "label": "Art. 477", "title": "Art. 477: Condiţii generale privind promovarea în funcţia publică", "slug": "art-477", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 477: Condi&#355;ii generale privind promovarea în func&#355;ia\npublic&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Promovarea în grad profesional\n&#351;i promovarea în clas&#259; nu sunt condi&#355;ionate de existen&#355;a\nunui post vacant.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_579612297\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1219\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_579612297\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Promovarea într-o func&#355;ie public&#259; de conducere\neste condi&#355;ionat&#259; de existen&#355;a unui post vacant.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}